@startuml
title BP-11 - Scholarship Configuration

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Finance Officer|
start
:Create scholarship program;
:Define eligibility scope;
:Define discount amount or percentage;
:Select applicable products or students;

|Platform|
:Validate tenant scope;
:Validate scholarship value;
:Validate applicable period;

if (Scholarship valid?) then (Yes)
  :Save scholarship configuration;
else (No)
  :Return validation error;
  stop
endif

|Billing Engine|
:Apply scholarship when generating obligation;
:Reduce obligation amount according to rule;

|Finance Officer|
:Review scholarship impact report;
stop

note right
Source of truth includes scholarship.
Current MVP code does not yet implement a dedicated scholarship module.
end note
@enduml
